{
  "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "开车从 A 地到 B 地，平均时速是总路程除以总时间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "这个平均变化率，在图像上就是连接起点终点的那条割线的斜率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "一个自然的问题是：路上有没有某个瞬间，恰好跑出这个平均速度？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "secant",
      "line_id": "sec-1",
      "filename": "secant-sec-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/secant-sec-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "割线斜率等于 f(b) 减 f(a)，再除以 b 减 a。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "secant",
      "line_id": "sec-2",
      "filename": "secant-sec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/secant-sec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "它衡量的是整个区间上，函数值的总体升降快慢。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "secant",
      "line_id": "sec-3",
      "filename": "secant-sec-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/secant-sec-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "而曲线上每一点的切线斜率，就是那一瞬间的导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "mvt",
      "line_id": "mvt-1",
      "filename": "mvt-mvt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/mvt-mvt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "拉格朗日中值定理说：只要函数连续又光滑，区间内必有一点 c。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "mvt",
      "line_id": "mvt-2",
      "filename": "mvt-mvt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/mvt-mvt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "在这一点，切线斜率恰好等于割线斜率，两条线彼此平行。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "mvt",
      "line_id": "mvt-3",
      "filename": "mvt-mvt-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/mvt-mvt-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "也就是说，瞬时变化率总会在某处追平平均变化率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "rolle",
      "line_id": "rolle-1",
      "filename": "rolle-rolle-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/rolle-rolle-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "如果两端点函数值相等，割线就变成水平线，斜率为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "rolle",
      "line_id": "rolle-2",
      "filename": "rolle-rolle-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/rolle-rolle-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "这时必有一点导数为零，那正是曲线的峰或谷，这就是罗尔定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "换一个函数或调整区间，红色割线会随之移动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "注意那条绿色切线始终与割线平行，中值点 c 也随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "中值定理保证平均变化率一定会被某个瞬时变化率取到。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "几何上，就是曲线上总有一点的切线平行于两端的割线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mean-value-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mean-value-theorem/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "罗尔定理是它水平时的特例，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 33.71,
  "total_size": 539568
}